elements.title: Miles of Plancy
elements.contents: ... that a contemporary chronicler does not dare say who assassinated Miles of Plancy (event pictured), but a later source implicates an in-law?

elements.title: 1862 Brooklyn riot
elements.contents: ... that the 1862 Brooklyn riot involved a mob mainly comprising Irish Americans targeting African-American workers at a tobacco factory?

elements.title: A Foreign Sound
elements.contents: ... that A Foreign Sound includes a song that Caetano Veloso called "a fake American song written by a Brazilian", and a song he called "a fake Brazilian song written by Americans"?
